  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">F</span> envision</p><p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per hour</p><p><strong>Trigger</strong> You use Spellstrike with a non-cantrip spell and miss with the Strike</p><p><strong>Effect</strong> An explosion of magical energy—stored up for the Spellstrike—explodes out. All creatures in a @Template[emanation|distance:5] take 1d6 damage per rank of the spell, with a @Check[reflex|against:spell|basic] save against your spell DC. This damage is the same type the spell would have dealt, and the activation gains that trait; if the spell would have dealt multiple types of damage, choose one of them. If the damage of the explosion is mental, the save is @Check[will|against:spell|basic] instead of Reflex.</p>"
    },
